💾 Backend 1: In-Memory Storage

Characteristics:
   • Fast: Direct memory access
   • Ephemeral: Data lost on shutdown
   • Simple: No configuration needed
   • Thread-safe: Built-in Spine protection

Created spine: 019b529f-2e88-7982-8b1e-3d398fdb77b6
   Storage: In-Memory
   Height: 1

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
💿 Backend 2: Sled Storage (Embedded DB)

Note: Sled backend available via feature flag
✅ Configuration: loam-spine-core with sled feature

Characteristics:
   • Persistent: Data survives restarts
   • Embedded: No separate database server
   • Transactional: ACID guarantees
   • Concurrent: Multi-threaded access

Usage in production:
   // With sled feature enabled:
   use loam_spine_core::storage::SledStorage;
   let storage = SledStorage::open("/data/loamspine")?;

